  "StockRole": "Skirmisher",
  "YangsThoughts": "The Remix is a one-of-a-kind machine, the first of three Project Rewrite designs commissioned by the Centrella granddaughter who took over leadership of the Rangers around 3080, built from a deliberate mix of Jihad-era Word of Blake salvage and Diamond Shark Clan technology. That combination is unusual enough on its own, but the Bloodhound Active Probe and Laser AMS together give it a defensive and sensor awareness package you rarely see on a skirmisher this size. It is a reserved-pilot machine, which tells you everything about how the Rangers value it.",
